        "TileImage": "$($repository 9b0d0651-4f81-40e5-bf2a-5aec6fd763a5).Image",
        "Description": "The elimination of the Corsican activated a dead man&apos;s switch. Edward Mendez, a military officer and weapons smuggler, is now set to launch a mobile drone strike targeting Sierra Knox&apos;s closest friend and alleged love interest. The late Corsican ensured that the only way to prevent the drone strike was Mendez&apos;s death by accidental or natural means. Eliminate Mendez, and the strike will be prevented, saving countless lives. The strike will commence in 2 minutes. No time to waste, 47. Good luck.",
